** An eclipse is when the sun and moon are in a position, so that they affect each others appearance.
   $ Solar Eclipse
   When the moon passes in front of the sun, from an earth observer perspective.
   Or, when the Earth passes into the moon's shadow.
   $ Lunar Eclipse.
   When the moon passes into the Earth's Shadow.
